an spiegel to keep sailing with bros amid snapchat stock dive former hedge fund billionaire philip falcone is selling his insane st barts estate for a cool  million the sprawling la grande maison des etoiles estate has nine bedrooms and  ¹₂ bathrooms three swimming pools and sweeping ocean views in the largest of the three pools is a glass pyramid that serves as the skylight for the stateoftheart fitness room below and thanks to falcone’s fashionista wife lisa maria five of the bedrooms are named for famous designers like hermès and christian dior the “louis vuitton” master suite has floor tiles arranged to resemble the designer’s logo stretching from the inroom pool area to the bathroom there’s also a caretaker cottage to house the staff falcone bought the estate in colombier’s exclusive gated area in  for  million — a record at the time for the island favored by business titans and hollywood celebs lisa maria told page six that they no longer spend much time at the estate “we’re selling it because our twin girls are now  and because of school and their activities we only get to come here a few weeks a year plus it needs a lot of upkeep and people keep asking to borrow it” the sale was first reported by the caribbean journal which did not identify the owner falcone ran as much as  billion at his hedge fund harbinger capital he made his fortune shorting subprime mortgages in  heading into the financial crisis in  the securities and exchange commission charged falcone with securities fraud he pleaded negligence and settled for  million agreeing to a fiveyear ban from the securities industry but admitting no wrongdoing he now runs hc holdings a publicly traded holding company the falcones famously bought penthouse founder bob guccione’s east th street townhouse for  million in  and completed an epic renovation which included a pool spa gym movie theater giant walkin wardrobe with a bar and two elevators they also considered installing heated sidewalks outside to avoid the inconvenience of shoveling snow the property is being offered exclusively by st barth properties sotheby’s international realty exclusive images provided by sotheby’s ad up next youtube star has fans lining up for new book fans lined up outside the barnes  noble in tribeca  view slideshow back continue share thisfacebooktwittergooglewhatsappemailcopy advertisement march   share thisfacebooktwittergooglewhatsappemailcopy filed under lisa maria falcone   phil falcone   real estate   st barts share this article share thisfacebooktwittergooglewhatsappemailcopy read next youtube star has fans lining up for new book read next youtube star has fans lining up for new book most popular this week  john heard found dead at   luann de lesseps’ marriage is hanging by a thread  mariah debuts a new look in vegas  linkin park frontman commits suicide  jennifer lawrence barfs at broadway show  was kanye involved with amanda lepore before kim k share selection now on congressman says cuomo is definitely running for president tom almost called off wedding to luann the day before ben affleck addresses rumors that he’s out as batman ceo disregards socialite status to direct busy traffic that time lil romeos k sesame street jewelry was stolen activists accuse la galleries on the rise of artwashing charlize theron reuniting with seth macfarlane for tv series royals celebrate prince georges birthday with adorable portrait dozens hospitalized during chance the rapper show hot felon and new girlfriend are a walking pdafest american idol winner cited for handgun at airport hulk hogans weekend turned sad and lonely pretty quick jimmey kimmel says baby is doing great after surgery heres whats going on in the nsync group text john heard found dead at  unabomber miniseries drawing plenty of buzz ahead of release issa rae my hoe phase was interrupted by real love rick ross is ready to take on the movie business guns n roses rocks the apollo theater bill murray performance mixes literature and